  <brief_title>Probiotics in the Management of Acute Rotavirus Diarrhea in Bolivian Children</brief_title>
  <official_title>Probiotics in the Management of Acute Rotavirus Diarrhea in Bolivian Children: Randomized Double-blind, Controlled Trial Using Two Different Preparations</official_title>
